name: Inquiry into the Sublime and Beautiful #03
description: "This artwork is the result of an intercontinental collaboration between JVDE (The Netherlands) and Helio Santos (México). both work with images from XVIII and XIX century, JVDE in photography and Helio with landscape painting, using AI and digital software manipulation to create new approximations and experiences" HEN 2021 .
